window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>Don't trust everyone you meet hereâ€¦</i></p> <p>A young British backpacker goes missing on the West Coast Trail.</p> <p>No one is sure whether she died or simply disappeared.</p> <p>Apart from Laura.</p> <p>Twenty years later, a body has been found.</p> <p>And there's only one person who could reveal the secret that Laura's been hiding all this time.</p> <p>But she knows that two can keep a secret.</p> <p>IF ONE OF THEM IS DEAD.</p> <p>A tense and suspenseful thriller perfect for fans of M.J. Ford and Susi Holliday.</p>"; 
